            <ul class="list">
              <li class="li"><span class="tick" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.2 16.2 4.9 12l1.4-1.4 2.9 2.9 8.6-8.6 1.4 1.4z"/></svg></span><span><span class="mono">meta</span>: title, description, canonical, og/twitter</span></li>
              <li class="li"><span class="tick" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.2 16.2 4.9 12l1.4-1.4 2.9 2.9 8.6-8.6 1.4 1.4z"/></svg></span><span><span class="mono">Schema.org</span>: Course + FAQPage + Organization + Breadcrumb</span></li>
              <li class="li"><span class="tick" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.2 16.2 4.9 12l1.4-1.4 2.9 2.9 8.6-8.6 1.4 1.4z"/></svg></span><span>Семантика заголовків: 1×H1, далі H2/H3</span></li>
              <li class="li"><span class="tick" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.2 16.2 4.9 12l1.4-1.4 2.9 2.9 8.6-8.6 1.4 1.4z"/></svg></span><span>A11y: skip link, aria-label, читабельні контрасти</span></li>
              <li class="li"><span class="tick" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.2 16.2 4.9 12l1.4-1.4 2.9 2.9 8.6-8.6 1.4 1.4z"/></svg></span><span>Форма з валідацією + UX-повідомленнями</span></li>
            </ul>

            <div class="chip-row" style="margin-top:12px">
              <span class="chip">performance</span>
              <span class="chip">structured data</span>
              <span class="chip">clean HTML</span>
              <span class="chip">no deps</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

